formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.	The Promoter of the firm has provided Customer ID, details of PAN / Aadhar Card, and Mobile Numbers of the allottees, 
2.	No registered agreement for sale is produced before us while giving this certificate by the promoter and copy of sale deed is produced by the promoter and in many cases, the promoter has given reply and submitted that the customers is not ready for registering agreement for sale and hence directly sale deed executed as per request of the customers. We have given and submitted the detail based on the self-certified copy Form 3A provided by the promoter.
3.	The amount received from the customer / allotees are not deposited in the RERA Bank Account by the promoter which is violation of Provision of GUJARAT RERA Act, 2016 so please follow the same and deposit the said amount in RERA Bank Account.
4.	As per information and explanation received from the promoter of the project, the promoter has sold plot of land i.e. plot to the customer as per market demand and requirement of the customers. The Promoter has taken affidavit form the customers for construction in this matter. The Promoter has prepared two documents i.e. sale of plot of land and construction agreement for transfer of property or units or house with the customers.
5.	The promoter has made default and not paid installment of Secured loan taken from DHFL Since Dec ? 2019 and no secured loan statement produced and now no interest expenses debited to profit and loss account and no interest paid by the promoter for last 2 to 3 years.
6.	189 units were booked at the time of Loan taken from DHFL and hence amount receivable i.e. pending against the sale of house, the bank has created mortgaged / hypothecated to DHFL. No NOC is produced before us hence in all units we have given the created status in Encumbrance Status of the units. We have given the detail of Encumbrance after certified and confirmed by the Promoter of the Project
7.	The detail of encumbrances of loan taken from DHFL is not updated on Gujarat RERA Website. But it is regularly reported in Form 3 by us for showing actual position of the project.
8.	It is the responsibility of management to prepare the financial statement of firm. The firm has prepared financial statement by following the mercantile method of accounting. The promoter has passed all necessary entries in accounts and reported all bank accounts in the financial statements and based on the unaudited accounts produced before us for given this certificate and relied on same for reporting to RERA Authority while certifying Form 3.
9.	The compilation & certification of figures in the said RERA Form - 3 along-with applicable annexure are based & relied on ?  
Latest Architects & Engineers certificates regarding estimated construction cost, Nos. of Garage/covered/Open parking as per RERA, Calculation of carpet area of each & every units of the said project as per RERA & Percentage of completion of on-site works, 
-	Duly signed plan passed, 
-	Previous years Audited financials, 
-	Duly certified provisional financials up to (31/05/2022), 
-	Duly certified secured and unsecured loans, estimated project cost & receivables from the allottee by the management of entity and; 
-	such other information & explanations provided by the entity & proprietor/partner/director of the Entity, 
which, to the best of our knowledge and belief were necessary for the purpose of issuing this certificate.
10.	We clarify that physical copy of Form No.3 & 3A contains certain explanatory and other notes to the various clauses which do not find place in the electronic Form No. 3 & 3A. In view of this, the electronic Form No.3 & 3A should be read together with all the notes appearing in the physical Form No.3 & 3A and in case of any conflict, the information and details provided in physical copy shall prevail.
11.	The promoter has directly registered Sale deed instead of agreement for sale registration hence in those cases, we have mentioned the Date of registration of Sale deed in that column.
